Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: General Douglas MacArthur and the Japanese surrender
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00ydpd6
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 16 Aug 1985
The 40th anniversary of the surrender of the Japanese at the end of the Second World War, the devastating hurricane in Galveston, Texas, and a profile of General Douglas MacArthur.